{"tid":2207233,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"港女塊野磨極都冇反應","createTime":"2020-09-18T04:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T08:31:05.000Z","uid":119572,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9fa1c604a972ce7611a8a66f93e9a107db3718b0","tid":2207233,"uid":119572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:39:45.000Z","msg":"平時見到班女臨俾錢個陣先慢慢係個散銀包到搵散銀都算，但見到人磨袋磨極都俾唔到錢真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日我真係極度懷疑班港女張八達通係特別啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到有條港女買嘢俾錢個陣，磨袋磨左十幾次，之後搵個長條型銀包出黎繼續磨都係唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後佢放棄左死死地氣搵張八達通出嚟，點知張八達通拍左幾次先得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母下次爽手啦"},{"pid":"8bf7f55cd75e0be5f4545a89e9dcc1f9dff80f11","tid":2207233,"uid":11809,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"張卡退化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33cba78511fff854e785998e57492bd7adacb72e","tid":2207233,"uid":68689,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T04:42:36.000Z","msg":"睇哂先知係講八達通 出返去先"},{"pid":"ddc0f9aa20c306cc5566c677d90004f0a227dbad","tid":2207233,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T05:13:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058877457aa4813346288fd060aada951934bfcf","tid":2207233,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T08:31:05.000Z","msg":"以為你做鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}